  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vending Machine Business Simulator is a simulation game where you start with very little money in your pocket and build a vending empire that spreads across the city. Work for others and once you have the necessary experience and money, start your own business.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Manage Your Machines:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998750/extras/8fe2306b17f6acd7a229286e06b961eb.poster.avif?t=1773637953\" width=610 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998750/extras/8fe2306b17f6acd7a229286e06b961eb.webm?t=1773637953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998750/extras/8fe2306b17f6acd7a229286e06b961eb.mp4?t=1773637953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase, place, and maintain vending machines across different locations. Keep track of inventory and ensure machines are stocked and operational.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Optimize Profits:</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998750/extras/718d4322e29a6c7c5bfedfa9d66964d0.poster.avif?t=1773637953\" width=610 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998750/extras/718d4322e29a6c7c5bfedfa9d66964d0.webm?t=1773637953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998750/extras/718d4322e29a6c7c5bfedfa9d66964d0.mp4?t=1773637953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow local events, adjust pricing strategies, and optimize product offerings to maximize revenue and profitability.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Expand Your Empire:</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998750/extras/35d4cbe0ebb585aa79e953b3e849f3ed.poster.avif?t=1773637953\" width=610 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998750/extras/35d4cbe0ebb585aa79e953b3e849f3ed.webm?t=1773637953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998750/extras/35d4cbe0ebb585aa79e953b3e849f3ed.mp4?t=1773637953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new locations and unlock new type of machines to attract more customers and increase sales.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dynamic Challenges:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998750/extras/64a9b10a2c4ad09df6fb03105d8a4537.poster.avif?t=1773637953\" width=610 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998750/extras/64a9b10a2c4ad09df6fb03105d8a4537.webm?t=1773637953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Overcome challenges such as machine malfunctions, aggressive customers, changing consumer trends, and economic changes.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Realistic Simulation:</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a realistic simulation of the vending machine business, including factors like machine maintenance, customer preferences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to embark on the journey to vending success?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vending Machine Business Simulator is a simulation game where you start with very little money in your pocket and build a vending empire that spreads across the city. Work for others and once you have the necessary experience and money, start your own business.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Manage Your Machines:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998750/extras/8fe2306b17f6acd7a229286e06b961eb.poster.avif?t=1773637953\" width=610 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998750/extras/8fe2306b17f6acd7a229286e06b961eb.webm?t=1773637953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998750/extras/8fe2306b17f6acd7a229286e06b961eb.mp4?t=1773637953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase, place, and maintain vending machines across different locations. Keep track of inventory and ensure machines are stocked and operational.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Optimize Profits:</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998750/extras/718d4322e29a6c7c5bfedfa9d66964d0.poster.avif?t=1773637953\" width=610 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998750/extras/718d4322e29a6c7c5bfedfa9d66964d0.webm?t=1773637953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998750/extras/718d4322e29a6c7c5bfedfa9d66964d0.mp4?t=1773637953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow local events, adjust pricing strategies, and optimize product offerings to maximize revenue and profitability.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Expand Your Empire:</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998750/extras/35d4cbe0ebb585aa79e953b3e849f3ed.poster.avif?t=1773637953\" width=610 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998750/extras/35d4cbe0ebb585aa79e953b3e849f3ed.webm?t=1773637953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998750/extras/35d4cbe0ebb585aa79e953b3e849f3ed.mp4?t=1773637953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new locations and unlock new type of machines to attract more customers and increase sales.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dynamic Challenges:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998750/extras/64a9b10a2c4ad09df6fb03105d8a4537.poster.avif?t=1773637953\" width=610 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998750/extras/64a9b10a2c4ad09df6fb03105d8a4537.webm?t=1773637953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Overcome challenges such as machine malfunctions, aggressive customers, changing consumer trends, and economic changes.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Realistic Simulation:</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a realistic simulation of the vending machine business, including factors like machine maintenance, customer preferences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to embark on the journey to vending success?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
